The paper deals with the problem of balancing performance and safety in autonomous vehicles, which is a common theme in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves online adaptation, which is also a key topic in the field of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses bandit optimization, which is a common technique in the field of multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
